      Which country is better, Vietnam or Indonesia?
      Vietnamese is great if you like history, culture or cheap things. Its geographical features and cultural heritage make it a region with a strictly South-Eastern experience. On the other hand Indonesia's natural wonders covered a multitude of attractions for any tourist interested in nature or adventure spirituality.4 Nov 2024

      What is the GDP per capita of Vietnam vs Indonesia?
